(20, 1, '2020-02-04 10:56:52', '2020-02-04 10:56:52', '<h3>Content Not Updated..</h3>\n<p><br /><br /><!--StartFragment--></p>\n\n<p><!--EndFragment--><br /><br /></p>', 'about us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-04 10:56:52', '2020-02-04 10:56:52', '', 7, 'http://localhost/lgmi_final/2020/02/04/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2020-02-04 11:00:58', '2020-02-04 11:00:58', '<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3> Building a Brighter Future for All</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> At Life Gate Ministries International, we’re raising funds and promoting initiatives to help those who need it most. With an array of fundraising events and volunteer projects, we welcome you to join our endeavours aimed at making the world a better place. Read on and contact us to learn how you can become part of the change.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LGMI Associate with teen challenge, Churches and others charity organisation is one of the world’s leading drug rehab centres with a very high success rate for helping people become free from drugs and alcohol. LGMI with Teen Challenge London is a 18-month, faith-based, residential drug rehabilitation programme located in East London which offers men aged 18+ freedom from drug and alcohol addiction. Based on Christian principles the programme offers spiritual and academic training, equipping individuals to return to society as responsible adults. Centres for women are available in Scotland &amp; Wales. See our directory of UK rehab centres.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LGMI with Teen Challenge holds a remarkable high documented cure rate. Statistics show that many secular government-funded drug rehabilitation programmes have less than a 10% success rate after treatment. Independent research in the United States has consistently shown that over 70% of Teen Challenge graduates have remained drug-free – when surveyed five years after graduation!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'welcome to l g m i', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-04 11:00:58', '2020-02-04 11:00:58', '', 11, 'http://localhost/lgmi_final/2020/02/04/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(22, 1, '2020-02-04 11:03:43', '2020-02-04 11:03:43', '<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>Lending a Helping Hand</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Inspired by a life-changing event, Life Gate Ministries International was established in 2010 in Kent, Aylesford, UK. Over the years, we have become one of the most trusted and effective limited Company by Guarranty foundations, working hard to improve the lives of those in need. Here you can learn more about who we are and what we do.We aim primarily to help men with drug and alcohol problems, who abuse substances on a daily or several times weekly basis. Our ladies centre is based in Wales.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our age group is 18+ years of age.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are an inclusive organisation, admitting men from a variety of ethnic and cultural backgrounds and men who have a faith or no faith.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We teach basic life skills, such as responsibility, good work habits, integrity, self-discipline and ethical morality.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We prepare our students to re-enter society as good employees, husbands &amp; fathers, functioning as ‘substance-free’ individuals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe strongly that as a man yields himself to God, he will change. We teach and counsel that God can change any life with an emphasis on daily practical application.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our counselling is Biblical in perspective which encourages men to function as caring and responsible adults.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our ministry is based upon a relationship with God through His Son, Jesus Christ, and the fellowship of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our programme is based on inter-denominational Christian teaching.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'who we are and what we do', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'who-we-are-and-what-we-do', '', '', '2020-02-12 10:06:51', '2020-02-12 10:06:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/lgmi_final/?page_id=22', 0, 'page', '', 0),
